msgid "Archer description"
msgstr ""
"As for long-distance influence, and reaching outside of our own circles,\n"
"the archer fills the important role of blogging, tweeting, iron-manning\n"
"and generally making a positive noise about Raku, which can reach people\n"
"far away."
